description: BRC4204-Crystal is the OG Ordinals NFT of BRC4204 protocol, and BRC4204 is the first AI-Meta-Protocol on Fractal Bitcoin. The holders of BRC4204-Crystal will enjoy future airdrop including the 1st native BRC4204 asset, token and more. BRC4204 introduced a new way to launch Assets on BTC called "AInscription" , which can lock the prompts within the Inscription block on Fractal Bitcoin network. Plus, BRC4204 will support fractional ownership of NFT, similar to ERC404.
name: BRC4204-Crystal
